snippet.title: KeepSynthin32
snippet.description: Hey! Welcome to my channel! My name is Felipe Forero. I am an 18 year old musician who plays guitar, bass, drums, and keys such as synthesizers and organs. I am a guitarist and I love teaching people how to play synthesizers since it's such a powerful instrument when done well. So, I hope you enjoy my videos and learn something!
